reviewText: I enjoyed listening to these mysteries as a high schooler.  I would listen religiously every week.  Howard Duff was one of my favorite radio actors of the time.  His voice was perfect for the part. I was disappointed when Humphrey Bogart got the part in the movies.  Of course, Bogart had the big name recognition.  But i was also disappointed that the movies  never found more big roles for Duff.
